Sharearchy: an open index founded in March 2009 to aggregate torrents and links available via open source, free, creative commons and public domain licenses.

To get up and running:
Install:
Ruby on Rails 2.3.2
MySQL
Sphinx

These gems:
mysql
authlogic
mislav-will_paginate

Add this to the crontab (bash$ crontab -e):
0 * * * * admin cd /home/admin/public_html/sharearchy.com/current && /usr/bin/rake RAILS_ENV=production thinking_sphinx:index >> /home/admin/public_html/sharearchy.com/shared/log/cron.log 2>&1